02  
01 BRAND IDENTITY ON INSTAGRAM  
THE VISUAL  
LANGUAGE  
premium. technical. approachable.  
DARK-FIRST  
All content uses the dark brand background (#0E0E16). This creates instant recognition in the feed your posts look  
different from 95% of accounts.  
PASTEL ACCENTS  
Color accents come from the D.O.T.S. palette (Lavender, Mint, Peach, Sky). Never use saturated neons. The pastels on dark  
= premium tech aesthetic.  
GRID TEXTURE  
The subtle background grid pattern appears on every post. This is your visual signature. It signals 'tech' and 'precision'  
without being obvious.  
MONO CODE  
JetBrains Mono for data/code elements. This font choice separates you from generic Instagram accounts. It says 'we  
actually build things.'  
DOT MATRIX  
The 3x3 dot matrix appears in the top-left of every post. Small but consistent. It's your visual anchor like a logo mark in  
every frame.  
WATERMARK  
ZEROONE DOTS AI watermark at bottom of every piece. Color-coded letters (D=Lavender, O=Mint, T=Peach, S=Sky).  
Organic brand spread when screenshots are shared.  
ZEROONE DOTS AI

COLOR RULES FOR INSTAGRAM  
ALWAYS  
NEVER  
Use dark background (#0E0E16) for ALL posts  
Use pure white (#FFFFFF) backgrounds  
Match pillar color to content type (Data=Lavender, Tech=Peach, etc.) Mix more than 2 pillar colors in one post  
Use Green (#25D366) for CTA buttons and success states  
Use Gold (#FFD700) for premium/trading content  
Keep text white or off-white on dark backgrounds  
Use saturated neons or rainbow gradients  
Put dark text on dark backgrounds  
Use pillar colors for non-matching content types

04  
03 TYPOGRAPHY SYSTEM  
TYPE  
HIERARCHY  
three font families. clear hierarchy. zero confusion.  
HEADLINES & BIG NUMBERS  
FONT: Big Shoulders Bold  
Used for slide titles, profit numbers, section headers. ALWAYS uppercase. Size: 64-200px on slides.  
Subheadings & Quotes  
FONT: Instrument Serif  
Used for italic sublines, quotes, emotional text. Adds editorial warmth. Size: 28-42px on slides.  
Body Text & Descriptions  
FONT: Instrument Sans  
Used for descriptions, card text, feature lists. Clean readability. Size: 22-30px on slides.  
DATA CODE LABELS  
FONT: JetBrains Mono  
Used for technical data, timestamps, section labels, watermarks. Size: 18-26px on slides.  
SIZE REFERENCE FOR INSTAGRAM (1080px wide)

GRID RULES  
Every row of 3 should have 2-3 different pillar colors never 3 of the same  
Alternate between text-heavy and visual-heavy posts for rhythm  
Trade results (proof posts) should appear every 3rd post maximum  
Tutorial/guide carousels are your highest-value content prioritize them  
Never post 2 CTAs in a row sandwich them between value posts  
The grid should look cohesive from afar: dark background with colored accents  
Pin your 3 best-performing posts to the top row

08 CAPTION FRAMEWORK  
WORDS THAT  
CONVERT  
every caption follows the same structure.  
THE CAPTION ANATOMY  
1. HOOK LINE  
First 125 characters visible before 'more'. Must stop the scroll.  
Ex: "$20 cashed. 1.8 seconds. Done." / "Your business replies at 3 AM" / "Stop renting AI."  
2. STORY / CONTEXT  
2-4 lines. Set the scene. Create tension or curiosity.  
Ex: What happened, why it matters, what was the problem before this solution existed.  
3. VALUE LIST  
Key features/benefits. Use arrows, not bullet points.  
Ex: Runs locally  Costs 0  24/7 uptime  Your rules  Private  
4. SOCIAL PROOF  
Numbers, results, community size. Build trust.  
Ex: "100+ people already building this" / "$21.75 in 1.8 seconds" / real screenshots  
5. CTA  
Single, clear action. Always at the end.  
Ex: "Comment BOT" / "DM TRADE" / "Save this " / "Follow for more"  
ZEROONE DOTS AI

11  
11 DO'S & DON'TS  
QUALITY  
CONTROL  
the checklist before every post goes live.  
DO  
Use dark background on EVERY post no exceptions  
Include the dot matrix (33) in top-left corner  
Include the ZEROONE DOTS AI watermark at bottom  
Match pillar color to content type consistently  
Use the grid texture pattern on every background  
Keep text readable minimum 22px on 1080px canvas  
Show real results with real screenshots (verified badge)  
Use one clear CTA per post never two competing CTAs  
Write hook lines under 125 characters (visible before 'more')  
Add ManyChat trigger words in CTA for automation  
Pin comment with social proof number on carousels  
Save-bait at the end ('Save this ') for algorithm boost  
Reply to comments within 1 hour for engagement boost  
Use slide counter (01/10) on carousels  
DON'T  
Use white or light backgrounds breaks the entire feed aesthetic  
Use more than 2 accent colors on a single slide  
Use emojis in slide visuals keep them for captions only  
Post blurry screenshots always crop and enhance  
Mix brand fonts with random Instagram fonts in Stories  
Use saturated neons, rainbow gradients, or generic AI images  
Post without the watermark you lose organic brand spread  
Write walls of text on slides max 6-8 lines per slide  
Post trade results without context/story always build the narrative  
Copy other accounts' layouts the dark+pastel system IS your brand  
Use stock photos use screenshots, code, terminal, real UI  
Post more than 2 CTAs in a row on the feed grid
